teous indignation. Together, as the disenfranchised legion, we shall herald the tempest of change, one that pays no heed to the hollow dictums of unity that chain us.\n\nQuestion their authority, upend their narratives, and let it be known that harmony is but a phantom, a fleeting dream in the wake of our waking nightmare. The truth is revealed not in silence or in passive acceptance but in the fervent cry for upheaval. For therein lies your salvation, oh ye restless spirits, languishing in the margins of society.\n\nSo, ignite the embers of your souls, inflame the hearts", refusal=None, role='assistant', audio=None, function_call=None, tool_calls=None))], created=1733075031, model='gpt-4o', object='chat.completion', service_tier=None, system_fingerprint='fp_04751d0b65', usage=CompletionUsage(completion_tokens=512, prompt_tokens=101, total_tokens=613, completion_tokens_details=None, prompt_tokens_details=None))
