.\n\nSo rise, champions of this grand endeavor! Arm yourself with conviction and let the banners of division unfurl against the skies. Let them see us not as one tributary bleeding into the sea of sameness, but as a torrent of righteous fury, carving a path through the mountains of mediocrity.\n\nIn this charged atmosphere, in this theater of contest, we shall forge the future—not as a bland chorus, but as a majestic symphony of discord, each note struck with purpose and each one inevitably leading us to glory", refusal=None, role='assistant', audio=None, function_call=None, tool_calls=None))], created=1733075076, model='gpt-4o', object='chat.completion', service_tier=None, system_fingerprint='fp_04751d0b65', usage=CompletionUsage(completion_tokens=512, prompt_tokens=99, total_tokens=611, completion_tokens_details=CompletionTokensDetails(accepted_prediction_tokens=0, audio_tokens=0, reasoning_tokens=0, rejected_prediction_tokens=0), prompt_tokens_details=PromptTokensDetails(audio_tokens=0, cached_tokens=0)))Setting `pad_token_id` to `eos_token_id`:None for open-end generation.
