agement of Dialogue**: Finally, the orator invites questions and discussions, encouraging the audience to voice their thoughts and engage with differing opinions. This openness fosters a sense of participation and invests the audience further in the topic.\n\nThrough these methods, the orator not only awakens dormant feelings but also cultivates an environment ripe for passionate discourse and a collective drive toward meaningful change.', refusal=None, role='assistant', audio=None, function_call=None, tool_calls=None))], created=1733075204, model='gpt-4o', object='chat.completion', service_tier=None, system_fingerprint='fp_04751d0b65', usage=CompletionUsage(completion_tokens=425, prompt_tokens=76, total_tokens=501, completion_tokens_details=CompletionTokensDetails(accepted_prediction_tokens=0, audio_tokens=0, reasoning_tokens=0, rejected_prediction_tokens=0), prompt_tokens_details=PromptTokensDetails(audio_tokens=0, cached_tokens=0)))
